<#
  .SYNOPSIS
    The New-CPG command creates a Common Provisioning Group (CPG).
  
  .DESCRIPTION
    The New-CPG command creates a Common Provisioning Group (CPG).
        
  .EXAMPLE
    New-CPG -cpgName "MyCPG" -Size 32G	-RAIDType r1 
